Pore	z L (e 0 )	1.00		
V L (mV)	307		
S4	z J (e 0 )	0.60		
V J (mV)	20		
RCK1	Kd 1 (μ m )	10.03		
RCK2	Kd 2 (μ m )	2.98		4820
S4-Pore	D 	3.34		
RCK1-Pore	C 1 	2.84	1.00	
RCK1-S4	E 1 	10.00		
